        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 60. Details of hemipenis of Macroscapha rehmi sp. nov., Macroscapha scotia sp. nov., and Macroscapha turbida (Müller, 1908). Macroscapha turbida (Müller, 1908): A–D, adult male (SNB 0344-DNA 81, ZMH K-41476). Macroscapha rehmi sp. nov.: E–H, paratype adult male (SNB 0025, ZMH K-40836). Macroscapha scotia sp. nov.: I–L, holotype adult male (SNB 0739, ZMH K-40820). A, entire hemipenis; B, F, J, conical, perforated process of copulatory rod; C, G, K, distal, short process of copulatory rod; D, H, L, lamelliform structure of copulatory rod; E, I, entire copulatory rod. Scale bars: A, E, I = 100 Mm; B–D, F–H, J–L = 50 Mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890197/files/figure.png" .

