        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 61. Hemipenis of Macroscapha rehmi sp. nov., Macroscapha scotia sp. nov., and Macroscapha turbida (Müller, 1908). Macroscapha turbida (Müller, 1908): A, B, paralectotype adult male (SNB 0747, ZMB 13133); C, adult male (SNB 0344-DNA 81); D, (SNB 0347-DNA 84), (ZMH K-41476). Macroscapha rehmi sp. nov.: E, holotype adult male (SNB 0744, ZMH K-41482); F, paratype adult male (SNB 0025); G, paratype adult male (SNB 0058); H, paratype adult male (SNB 0026) (ZMH K-40836); I, paratype adult male (SNB 0742, ZMH K-40836). Macroscapha scotia sp. nov.: J, paratype adult male (SNB 0022); K, paratype adult male (SNB 0027); L, paratype adult male (SNB 0738); M, paratype adult male (SNB 0739) (ZMH K-40837). Scale bar = 100 Mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890199/files/figure.png" .

